sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Chromatin was sonicated by Bioruptor (Diagenode, Belgium) under the condition as follows: 20 cycles of 30 s on, 60 s off. The sonicated chromatin was spun down at 12,000 rpm for 10 min at 4 °C to collect the chromatin. Add antibody (10 μg) to the soluble chromatin (80 μg), and incubate at 4 °C with rotation overnight. Protein A/G Dynabeads (10 μl of beads per 1 μg of antibody, Life Tech, 10004D) were washed three times with Low Salt Wash Buffer. The washed Dynabeads were added to the soluble chr ...
sample_data_processing: The adaptors were cut using Ngmerge, Pair-end reads were aligned to hg38 genome using bowtie2 under default parameter setting, The TF binding sites were detected by macs2

sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Place frozen tissue into a pre-chilled 2 ml Dounce with 2 ml cold nuclei lysis buffer. Allow frozen tissue to thaw for 5 minutes. Dounce with A pestle until resistance goes away ( 10 strokes). Dounce with B pestle for 20 strokes. Pre-clear larger chunks by pelleting at 100 RCF for 1 min in a pre-chilled centrifuge.Count nuclei using Trypan blue staining and aliquot nuclei for ATAC reaction. Harvest and count cells (counting protocol to be de_ned by the user; see APPENDIX3F). Cells should be inta ...
sample_data_processing: The adaptors were cut using Ngmerge, Pair-end reads were aligned to hg38 genome using bowtie2 under default parameters, The open chromation regions were detected by macs2 using the setting of "--nomodel --shift -37 --extsize 73 --keep-dup all -q 0.05 --broad"

Pre-clear larger chunks by pelleting at 100 RCF for 1 min in a pre-chilled centrifuge.Count nuclei using Trypan blue staining and aliquot nuclei for ATAC reaction. Harvest and count cells (counting protocol to be de_ned by the user; see APPENDIX3F). Cells should be inta ...
sample_data_processing: The adaptors were cut using Ngmerge, Pair-end reads were aligned to hg38 genome using bowtie2 under default parameters, The open chromation regions were detected by macs2 using the setting of "--nomodel --shift -37 --extsize 73 --keep-dup all -q 0.05 --broad"
